<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy - ABC Retailers</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c3e50, #1a2530);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px 0;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 5px solid #3498db;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

            header h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

            header p {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
                max-width: 800px;
                margin: 0 auto;
                opacity: 0.9;
            }

        .content-wrapper {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .policy-content {
            flex: 2;
            min-width: 300px;
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        }

        .media-content {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 300px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin: 25px 0 15px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e8e8e8;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #3498db;
            margin: 20px 0 10px;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        ul, ol {
            margin-left: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        strong {
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        .contact-info {
            background: #e8f4fc;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #3498db;
        }

        .media-container {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

            .media-container h2 {
                text-align: center;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
                color: #2c3e50;
            }

        .video-wrapper, .map-wrapper {
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .video-wrapper {
            padding-top: 56.25%; /* 16:9 Aspect Ratio */
        }

        .map-wrapper {
            height: 400px;
        }

        iframe {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            border: none;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            margin-top: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .effective-date {
            text-align: center;
            font-style: italic;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #7f8c8d;
        }

        .mobile-adjust {
            width: 100%;
        }

            .mobile-adjust .media-container {
                width: 100%;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .mobile-adjust .video-wrapper,
            .mobile-adjust .map-wrapper {
                width: 100%;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p>Your privacy is important to us. This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information.</p>
        </header>

        <div class="content-wrapper">
            <div class="policy-content">
                <h1>Introduction</h1>
                <p>ABC Retailers is committed to protecting the privacy of our customers. This privacy policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you shop on our website.</p>

                <h1>Information We Collect</h1>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> We collect personal information, such as your name, email address, phone number, and shipping address, when you create an account or make a purchase.</li>
                    <li><strong>Payment Information:</strong> We collect payment information, such as credit card numbers, when you make a purchase.</li>
                    <li><strong>Browsing Information:</strong> We collect browsing information, such as your IP address, browser type, and device type, when you visit our website.</li>
                </ul>

                <h1>How We Use Your Information</h1>
                <ol>
                    <li><strong>Order Fulfillment:</strong> We use your personal and payment information to process and fulfill your orders.</li>
                    <li><strong>Communication:</strong> We use your contact information to communicate with you about your orders, promotions, and other updates.</li>
                    <li><strong>Marketing:</strong> We may use your information to send you marketing emails and promotions, but you can opt-out at any time.</li>
                    <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> We use browsing information to analyze website traffic and improve our services.</li>
                </ol>

                <h1>Information Sharing</h1>
                <ol>
                    <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> We share your information with service providers, such as payment processors and shipping companies, to fulfill your orders.</li>
                    <li><strong>Partners:</strong> We may share your information with partners, such as affiliates, to offer you relevant promotions.</li>
                    <li><strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> We may disclose your information if required by law or to protect our rights.</li>
                </ol>

                <h1>Security Measures</h1>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Encryption:</strong> We use encryption to protect your payment information.</li>
                    <li><strong>Secure Servers:</strong> We store your personal information on secure servers that are protected by firewalls and intrusion detection systems.</li>
                    <li><strong>Access Control:</strong> We limit access to your information to authorized personnel only.</li>
                </ul>

                <h1>Your Rights</h1>
                <ol>
                    <li><strong>Access:</strong> You can access and update your personal information by logging into your account.</li>
                    <li><strong>Opt-out:</strong> You can opt-out of marketing emails by clicking on the unsubscribe link.</li>
                    <li><strong>Delete:</strong> You can request to delete your account and personal information by contacting us.</li>
                </ol>

                <h1>Changes to this Policy</h1>
                <p>We may update this policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the updated policy on our website.</p>

                <div class="contact-info">
                    <h2><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Contact Us</h2>
                    <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this policy, please contact us at <strong>abcretailers@imail.co.za</strong>.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="effective-date">
                    <p>This policy is effective as of 1st September 2025.</p>
                </div>

                <p>By shopping on our website, you agree to the terms of this privacy policy.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="media-content">
                <div class="media-container">
                    <h2><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i> Privacy Explained</h2>
                    <div class="video-wrapper">
                        <iframe width="360" height="215" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/YmzatOYykHw?si=_5gpk2utBNmjL-Vm" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="media-container">
                    <h2><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> Our Location</h2>
                    <div class="map-wrapper">
                        <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3580.2513529192142!2d28.025748475414687!3d-26.188500577086238!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x1e950c0fb3a9cff7%3A0x1b322c95985f4b1d!2sPlanetarium%2C%201%20Jan%20Smuts%20Ave%2C%20Braamfontein%2C%20Johannesburg%2C%202017!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sza!4v1756719431173!5m2!1sen!2sza" width="600" height="450" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <footer>
            <p>&copy; 2025 ABC Retailers. All rights reserved.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>

    <script>

        function adjustLayout() {
            const screenWidth = window.innerWidth;
            const mediaContent = document.querySelector('.media-content');
            const policyContent = document.querySelector('.policy-content');

            if (screenWidth < 768) {
                document.body.classList.add('mobile-adjust');
            } else {
                document.body.classList.remove('mobile-adjust');
            }
        }

        // Initial adjustment
        adjustLayout();

        // Adjust on window resize
        window.addEventListener('resize', adjustLayout);
    </script>
</body>
</html>